      h4 Our awesome photographer Inge Kathleen, 
        a(href='http://www.ingekathleen.com/', target='_blank') visit her site.
      h5 Kayla Jones and Brian Hiatt for developing this site.
        
    .col-md-6.contact#contact
      a(href='http://nashvillesoftwareschool.com/'): img.nss-logo(src='/public/assets/nss.png', alt='nss')
